2026-05-13T17:35:38.4787410Z 13    <!--
2026-05-13T17:35:38.4787963Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T17:35:38.4788853Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-13T17:35:38.4790030Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-13T17:35:38.4790906Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-13T17:35:38.4791817Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
